    {
      "id": "t80",
      "tag": "div",
      "text": "Norway and Germany consistently top the list, with CPMs of $20–$40. The US follows closely at $12–$30, driven by its massive advertiser ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "id": "t81",
      "tag": "button",
      "text": "Why does India have such a low YouTube CPM?"
    },
    {
      "id": "t82",
      "tag": "div",
      "text": "India has enormous viewership but a less developed digital ad market and lower consumer purchasing power, making it less attractive to premium advertisers."
    },
    {
      "id": "t83",
